description.en:
Can assess the impact of the globalization process on different economic fields;
Can see the interconnections between the general tendencies of global economy and the development strategies of the Estonian economy;
Can assess the impacts of different economic policy instruments on an economy;
Has skills for acting in an integrating world.
Can assess the impacts of possible Estonia's development strategies on his/her own field of activities;
Has ideas for choosing the development strategy for a small country;
Can use economic policy instruments
